# Flatten

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:image, "~> 0.52"},
  {:req, "~> 0.5"},
  {:kino, "~> 0.14"}
])
```

## 画像の読込

```elixir
original_img =
  "https://www.elixirconf.eu/assets/images/drops.svg"
  |> Req.get!()
  |> Map.get(:body)
  |> Image.from_binary!()
```

## 背景の塗りつぶし

```elixir
Image.flatten!(original_img)
```

```elixir
Image.flatten!(original_img, background_color: :blue)
```
